记者从河南省长垣市公安局获悉，涉事“黑”作坊负责人已被警方刑事拘留。
The reporter learned from the Changyuan Public Security Bureau in Henan Province that the person in charge of the "black" workshop had been detained by the police on criminal charges.
然而，在警方切断了这一条假冒伪劣口罩的生产线后，湖南、湖北、河南、安徽、辽宁等地有消费者反映，自己购买到疑似假冒的“飘安”口罩。
However, Hunan, Hubei, Henan, Anhui, Liaoning and other places reported that they had bought suspected fake "fluttering" masks after police cut off the production line for the fake masks.
全文3354字，阅读约需6.6分钟▲湖南长沙市场流入的假冒伪劣“飘安”口罩，用手轻扯即破。
Full text 3354 words, reading about 6.6 minutes Changsha City, Hunan Province, the inflow of fake "fluttering" masks, with a light hand pull that broke.
受访者供图薄薄一层如纱般的口罩，未经任何杀菌消毒，被工人们徒手装进印有“河南飘安集团有限公司”字样的包装袋中。
Respondents were given a thin veil of gauze-like masks which were packed with the words "Henan Piao An Group Limited" by workers without any sterilization.
这是近日在网络上引发关注的一段视频，生产口罩的作坊内阴暗嘈杂，原材料和半成品散落一地，卫生状况令人担忧。
This is a recent video on the Internet, the production of masks in the dark and noisy workshops, raw materials and semi-finished products scattered on the ground, a worrying health situation.
新京报记者从河南省长垣市公安局获悉，涉事“黑”作坊负责人已被警方刑事拘留。
The Beijing News reporter learned from the Changyuan Public Security Bureau in Henan Province that the person in charge of the "black" workshop had been detained on criminal charges by the police.
然而，在警方切断了这一条假冒伪劣口罩的生产线后，湖南、湖北、河南、安徽、辽宁等地有消费者反映，自己购买到疑似假冒的“飘安”口罩。
However, Hunan, Hubei, Henan, Anhui, Liaoning and other places reported that they had bought suspected fake "fluttering" masks after police cut off the production line for the fake masks.
新京报记者了解到，目前多地公安、市场监管部门接到消费者投诉后介入调查，并对涉事商户进行查处。
Xinjing News reporter learned that many public security, market supervision departments have received complaints from consumers to intervene in the investigation, and the business involved in the investigation and punishment.
其中，河南省长垣市检察院对7名制售假冒伪劣口罩者批准逮捕。
Among them, Changyuan City Procuratorate in Henan Province seven people who produce and sell fake and inferior masks approved the arrest.
▲长垣警方捣毁的假冒伪劣口罩生产小作坊，无任何杀菌消毒设备。
Changyuan police destroyed the fake and low-quality mask production workshops, no sterilization equipment.
视频截图━━━━━药店所售口罩一扯即破，消费者举报连日来，北京、湖南、湖北、河南、四川、安徽、沈阳等地的消费者向新京报记者反映，他们在药店或超市买到了疑似假“飘安”牌口罩。
Video Interview - Drug stores sell masks at once, and consumers report that in recent days consumers in Beijing, Hunan, Hubei, Henan, Sichuan, Anhui and Shenyang have reported buying fake fluttering masks at pharmacies or supermarkets.
2月4日，湖北麻城的胡先生告诉新京报记者，其日前在当地一家药店购买了一包一次性口罩，透明的包装袋上印有两条交叉的蓝色条纹，口罩品牌及名称显示为“飘安”牌一次性使用口罩，每包20只，每只口罩多为薄薄一层，如薄纱一般，手轻轻一扯即破。
Mr. Hu told the Beijing News on Feb. 4 that he had bought a disposable mask at a local drugstore with clear blue stripes on it. The name and brand of the mask showed "Piao An" on a disposable mask of 20 masks, each with a thin film and a soft tear on the hand.
胡先生表示，当地还有其他药店售卖此类口罩。
Mr. Hu said other local pharmacies were selling such masks.
2月1日，他向市场监督管理局报案。
On 1 February, he reported the incident to the Market Surveillance Authority.
当时麻城市市场监督管理局工作人员回复称，其买的是假冒伪劣口罩，目前费用已经退还，涉事商户也已受到处罚。
Officials at the Massachusetts Institute of Market Supervision responded that they had bought fake masks, that the fees had been refunded and that the traders involved had been punished.
对于假冒口罩来源，当地仍在调查。
The origin of the fake masks is still under investigation locally.
2月5日，家住北京丰台区的孙先生告诉新京报记者，为做好疫情预防，他于1月23日下午，在丰台翠林小区东门元亨利康大药房，共花费56元购买了两袋“飘安”一次性口罩，每袋有10多只，颜色分别为紫色和蓝色。
On February 5, Mr. Sun, who lives in Fengtai District of Beijing, told the Beijing News that he had spent 56 yuan on two bags of fluttering disposable masks, each in purple and blue, on the afternoon of January 23 at Henrykang Pharmaceutical Co., the East Gate of the Cuilin District of Fengtai.
孙先生说，起初自己并未在意口罩数量、生产厂家以及薄厚程度，后来在看到相关新闻报道后，发现自己购买的口罩疑似假冒伪劣。
Mr. Sun said he didn't care about the number of masks, the manufacturer or the thickness of the mask.
经检查，他购买的口罩包装未印生产日期和保质期，也没有检验合格证。
Upon examination, the mask he purchased was not packaged with a production date and expiry date, nor was there a certificate of conformity.
新京报记者注意到，上述受访者购买的“飘安”口罩包装袋上印有河南飘安集团有限公司联系方式。
The Beijing News reporter noticed that the above-mentioned interviewees bought "fluttering an" Mask Pack with the contact information of Henan Piao'an Group Co. Ltd.
记者拨通电话后，对方称其并未生产过该包装及该颜色的口罩，认为消费者购买的口罩为假冒伪劣产品。
After dialing the phone, the other side said that it did not produce the packaging and the color of the mask, consumers buy a fake products.
目前，孙先生已经向北京市12345市民热线举报，等待相关部门处理。
At present, Mr. Sun has reported to the Beijing 12345 Citizen's Hotline and is waiting for the relevant departments to handle it.
▲孙先生在元亨利康大药房购买的“飘安”口罩只有一层。
Mr. Sun bought the "fluttering" mask at the Henry Connaught School of Pharmacy on only one floor.
受访者供图━━━━━药店：上架销售前未检验，已报警市民姜女士说，1月23日傍晚，她在北京市朝阳路百好堂大药房七分店购买了四包“飘安”口罩共计80元。
2007-9-24 16: 16 [hide] www.youtheme.cn Before putting on shelves for sale, Ms. Jiang, a citizen who had been called to the police, said she had bought four bags of "fluttering" masks for 80 yuan at seven branches of the Baohetang Pharmacy in Chaoyang Road, Beijing on the evening of January 23.
口罩质地同样只有薄薄一层，无防菌作用。
Mask texture is also only a thin layer, no antibacterial effect.
对此，涉事百好堂大药房母公司——北京百好堂医药经营有限公司一名负责人回应称，由于疫情蔓延，药店内的口罩一时间变得紧俏甚至脱销。
In response, a director of the Beijing Baihetang Pharmaceutical Company, the parent company, said: 'Because of the spread of the epidemic, the face masks in pharmacies are becoming tight and even out of stock.
公司方面从批发商处购进口罩后，未严格检查便上架销售，目前已开始召回，消费者持购买口罩凭证和口罩到其连锁药店，工作人员均会处理。
The company bought masks from wholesalers and sold them on shelves without strict inspection. They are now being recalled and consumers are buying masks and masks at their drugstore chains.
“我们也是受害者。
"We are also victims.
”上述负责人表示，目前其公司针对假冒伪劣“飘安”口罩一事已经向市场监督管理局和公安报案，正在等待执法部门追查口罩生产窝点和具体处理结果。
The official said the company had reported the case to the market watchdog and the public security department and was waiting for law enforcement to track down where the masks were manufactured and what the results would be.
新京报记者向涉事药店所在地的市场监管部门以及北京市12345市民热线反映，对方表示目前正在调查。
The Beijing News reported to the market regulator where the drugstore in question was located, as well as to the Beijing 12345 Citizen's Hotline, which said it was investigating.
▲电商平台上有商户售卖“飘安”口罩，并称假一赔十。
Electric business platform there are merchants selling "fluttering" masks, and said a fake 10.
网络截图━━━━━有电商涉嫌逃避平台监管售卖假口罩除了线下超市、药店，部分电商及微商也涉嫌售卖假冒伪劣口罩。
Internet Snapshot - There are suspected electrical operators evading the platform's regulation to sell fake masks. Apart from off-line supermarkets, pharmacies, some electrical vendors and micro-merchants are also suspected of selling fake and inferior masks.
北京市民孙先生告诉新京报记者，1月25日，其妻子在某电商平台上的一家名为“伊睿雅配饰专营店”里购买了“飘安”牌口罩，98元1包，20只装。
Beijing citizen Sun told the Beijing News that on January 25, his wife bought "Piao An" mask, 98 yuan a bag and 20 pieces in a special store called "Yiyuer Accessories" on an electrical business platform.
之后，关注了相关新闻报道，发现所购口罩与报道中的假冒口罩基本一致。
Afterwards, following the relevant news reports, found that the purchase of masks and reports of counterfeit masks are basically the same.
孙先生说，其事后联系涉事网店反映该问题，但对方一直为系统回复。
Mr. Sun said the company contacted the store to report the problem, but the other party has been responding to the system.
“就是希望商家召回口罩，平台和执法部门对商户做出处罚，并追查货源。
"The hope is that businesses recall masks, the platform and law enforcement departments to impose penalties on merchants, and trace the source of goods.
”2月2日至4日，新京报记者注意到，涉事电商仍正常营业，但已将所有口罩下架。
From February 2 to 4, the Beijing News reporter noticed that the electricity company in question was still operating normally, but had pulled all the masks off the shelves.
对于孙先生反映的情况，涉事电商的人工客服回应称正在处理。
As for the situation reported by Mr. Sun, the man-made customer service response of the telegraph company involved said it was being processed.
2月6日下午，某电商平台客服表示，孙先生的情况会转交专员处理。
On the afternoon of February 6, a customer service officer of an electric business platform said that Mr. Sun's situation would be referred to the Commissioner.
此外，新京报记者以“飘安”“飘安口罩”为关键词在多家电商平台上检索，发现平台已经对关键词相关的商品屏蔽或下架。
In addition, the Beijing News reporter "fluttering an" "fluttering mask" as the key words in a number of electronic commerce platforms, found that the platform has related to the keyword shielding or shelf.
还有电商平台发布“口罩禁令”，截至2月4日，永久清退15家涉嫌销售问题口罩店铺，并将5家商铺移交执法机关处理。
As of February 4, 15 shops suspected of selling problem masks were permanently removed and 5 shops were handed over to law enforcement agencies for processing.
新京报记者注意到，即使在这种情况下，仍有电商通过变更商品信息、错开关键词等销售假“飘安”口罩，所售口罩颜色各异，有黑色、粉红色、黄色等，甚至还有商家在商品详情页面标出假一赔十、七天无理由退货字样。
Even under such circumstances, the Beijing News noted, there are still electrical operators selling fake "fluttering" masks in various colors, including black, pink and yellow, by changing commodity information and staggered key words. There are even signs on the product details page that say "no reason to return" for 10 or 7 days.
新京报记者就上述情况向电商平台客服反映，对方表示将会处理相关问题。
The Beijing News reporter on the above-mentioned information to the electric business platform customer service, said the other side will deal with related issues.
▲某电商平台商户修改商品信息，逃避平台关键词监管。
A business platform merchants modify commodity information to avoid the platform keyword supervision.
网络截图━━━━━超200万只假飘安口罩流入市场被查有关假“飘安”牌口罩流入市场一事，新京报记者梳理发现，1月29日，浙江省台州市椒江区市场监督管理局根据相关线索对某医疗器械有限公司进行检查，发现24万只假“飘安”口罩，并予以查扣；1月30日，安徽省肥东县市场监管局接群众举报，对合肥市玉永大药房连锁有限公司肥东三店正在销售的假冒伪劣“飘安”口罩进行查扣。
More than 2 million fake Flying Ang masks were found entering the market. The Beijing News reports that on January 29, the Bureau of Market Supervision of Jiaojiang District, Taizhou, Zhejiang Province, inspected a medical device limited company and found 240,000 fake "fluttering" masks.
此外，河南漯河、辽宁桓仁、福建莆田以及湖南长沙均查出假“飘安”口罩流入市场并销售。
In addition, Henan Luohe, Huanren Liaoning, Putian in Fujian and Changsha in Hunan Province have all detected the entry of fake "fluttering" masks into the market and sold them.
2月5日下午，新京报记者从湖南省长沙市警方了解到，在警方近日侦办的假冒伪劣口罩案件中，涉及已销售的假冒伪劣“飘安”口罩近200万只。
February 5 afternoon, the Beijing News reporters from Changsha City, Hunan Province, police learned that the police recently investigated the case of fake and low-quality masks, involving the sale of fake "Flying Ann" Mask nearly 2 million.
长沙警方举例介绍，1月23日，长沙市高桥医药流通园康美源保健品店店主张某光为牟取暴利，在明知是假货的情况下，以0.3元/只的价格，从非法渠道购进假冒伪劣的飘安牌医用口罩106万只。
Changsha police gave an example, on January 23, Changsha Gao Qiao medical circulation Yuan Kang Mei Yuan health food store advocated a certain light for profiteering, in the knowledge that it is fake goods, at 0.3 yuan / price, from illegal channels to purchase fake Fa'an medical mask 1.06 million.
次日，张某光转手以0.75元至1元/只的价格将106万只口罩销售至长沙、娄底、岳阳、衡阳等地的多个下线客户，销售金额达到78万余元，非法获利45万余元。
The following day, Zhang changed hands and sold 1.06 million masks to multiple lower-line customers in Changsha, Lou di, Yueyang and Hengyang at a price of between 0.75 yuan and 1 yuan per lamp, with sales of more than 780,000 yuan and illegal profits of more than 450,000 yuan.
之后，这些口罩流入诊所、药店、超市以及微商的手中。
The masks were then poured into clinics, pharmacies, supermarkets and microbusinesses.
目前，警方将该案的5名犯罪嫌疑人控制，并查获5家售假门店。
At present, the police will be the case of five suspects in control, and seized five fake stores.
▲湖南长沙警方将销售假口罩的犯罪嫌疑人控制。
Changsha police in Hunan Province will sell fake mask suspects control.
受访者供图针对有人通过微信销售假冒口罩的情况，长沙警方介绍，在另一起案件中，警方查明：犯罪嫌疑人张某将85万只假冒伪劣飘安牌医用口罩以0.06元/只的价格销售给高桥大市场新政百货的经营者匡某，匡某以0.12元至0.25元/只的价格销售给崔某奎和刘某，崔某奎又以1元/只的价格销售给刘某凡，刘某凡再以3元/只的价格通过微信进行销售。
In another case, police found that the suspect Zhang sold 850,000 fake and shoddy medical masks to operators Quan Hong of Takahashi Big Market at a price of 0.12 yuan to 0.25 yuan per person.
警方介绍，这些假冒伪劣口罩只有极为轻薄的两层疑似纸浆层，没有防护层，无法起到有效防护的作用。
Police said that these fake mask only very light two-layer suspected of pulp, no protective layer, can not play an effective role in protection.
目前，该案6名犯罪嫌疑人被控制，4家售假门店被查，涉及已销售的假冒医用口罩85万只。
Currently, six suspects in the case are under control and four fake stores have been identified, involving 850,000 counterfeit medical masks that have been sold.
目前，该案仍在进一步侦办中。
The case is still under further investigation.
━━━━━河南长垣7名嫌疑人被批捕河南长垣被称为“中国医疗耗材之都”。
--Henan Changyuan Seven suspects have been arrested in Changyuan, Henan province, which is called the "Capital of Medical Supplies in China."
据央视报道，疫情发生后，河南长垣为了保障医用口罩和防护服的供应，70多家医用口罩生产企业召回员工。
After the outbreak, more than 70 medical mask manufacturers in Henan recalled their staff to ensure the supply of medical masks and protective clothing, CCTV reported.
位于长垣的河南飘安集团有限公司官网显示，其公司生产的医疗卫生产品销售量占市场份额48％以上。
The company's sales volume of medical and health products accounts for more than 48 percent of the market, according to the website of Changyuan-based Piao'an Group Co. Ltd.
据河南飘安集团有限公司发布的声明，其生产的口罩以蓝色为主，少量白色，没有生产过粉色口罩，该集团生产的正规口罩名称为“一次性使用医用口罩”，产品包装数量都是10只，假冒的口罩名称是“一次性使用口罩”，每包为20只装，且每只正规“飘安”口罩上都有“PIAOAN”字样。
According to a statement issued by Henan Piao'an Group Co., Ltd., the company produces face masks in blue, a small amount of white, no pink masks. The group produces a regular mask called 'disposable medical mask,' which comes in 10 packs, each with a 20-pack name, and 'PIAOAN' written on each regular mask.
此前，河南飘安集团有限公司配合当地警方和市场监管部门查处多处“黑”窝点，警方对涉事人员做出刑事拘留的措施，并追查已售口罩数量。
Earlier, Henan Piao An Group Co. Ltd. and local police and market regulatory authorities to deal with a number of "black" nest, the police officers involved in criminal detention measures, and to trace the number of masks sold.
2月5日，新京报记者从长垣市公安局获悉，2月4日21时，周某、谢某杰、张某辉、张某超、李某敏、苏某松、付某鑫等7人，分别因涉嫌销售假冒注册商标的商品罪、假冒注册商标罪被长垣市人民检察院依法批准逮捕，现羁押于长垣市看守所。
At 2100 hours on February 4, Zhou, Xie, Zhang Meihui, Zhang Min, Li Min, Su Mingsong and Fu Xin were arrested by the Changyuan People's Procuratorate on suspicion of selling goods with fake registered trademarks and counterfeiting of registered trademarks.
